To clarify, both tf.layers.conv2d and slim.conv2d should check that the rank is 4D and raise an error otherwise.
Using conv2d in a 5D tensor is out of the current API, but it can be implemente with reshapes.

body:
To clarify, both tf.layers.conv2d and slim.conv2d should check that the rank is 4D and raise an error otherwise.
Using conv2d in a 5D tensor is out of the current API, but it can be implemente with reshapes.
